data.description: Classic East Harriet brick charm with freshly refinished hardwoods in highly desirable lakes area location. This spacious condo with dining room built-ins, large eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances and updated cabinets/countertops, tile bath with clawfoot tub, and big primary bedroom closet with organizer make it the perfect move-in ready flat that you can call home. Don't worry about parking as this property includes a RARE one-car garage. Other amenities - on-site laundry, workout room, and multiple locked storage spaces. Access to the Minneapolis Lakes and Trail systems, restaurants, entertainment, and parks are right outside your door. With Bryant Ave reconstruction wrapping up in October, search Bryant Ave Reconstruction for the improvements and benefits! Rental of the unit is permitted.
